metadata.name: Lena
metadata.description:
My original character, Lena, is one of the dimensional overseer dragons. 
Although she may look calm and composed, if you look closely, you will see the destruction of other universes reflected in her eyes. 
Do the fallen flower petals symbolize the departure of other worlds? 
Let's just hope that our universe's turn never comes.
I would like to continue to draw illustrations of Lena. 
Please keep an eye on me.

2625 * 3770 pixel 300dpi
created by 2GONG
